Next power session is scheduled for this week. We will punch, we will jump, we will shape those bodies :)

Photo by bruce mars from Pexels

General warm-up

  • 5 minutes run

Round 1

  • Plank jump with side plank
  • Leg raises

Round 2

  • Open chest Jack
  • Hip raises in Crab

Round 3

  • High knee Jabs
  • Cross Squats

Round 4

  • In & Out abs with knee tap
  • Lunge with back leg raise (weight)

Round 5

  • Upper cut Jabs
  • Standing crunch with leg raise

Round 6

  • Wide jumps
  • Candle hip push

Round 7

  • Praying monk
  • Rotation crunch

Round 8

  • Side plank jumps
  • Bridge kicks

Bonus

  • Jab, Jab, Jump, Jump
  • Circle punch

Cool down

  • General stretching
